Mazzoni, }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Il canto VI dell'"Inferno"}{\plain \fs24 \f1  in }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Nuove letture dantesche}{\plain \fs24 \f1  (Florence: Le Monnier, 1967), p. \softline
19, points out that in the third book of Andreas Cappellanus' }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 De amore}{\plain \fs24 \f1  love between in-laws was \softline
